If you have encountered an error, but weren\'t able to report the error at the time (or you simply want to add a personal note on the matter), you can send me an email directly by clicking the link below.

I will read any error reports I receive, so please enter as many details as you can. eg. If you encountered a problem while reading an image/archive, sending me information about the file, such as its size, format, etc. (or the file itself) would help tremendously.

By default, JComic will include the make and model of your device, the version of Android you are running, and the version of JComic you are using. JComic m\'enverra automatiquement le modèle de l\'Android que vous utilisez, ainsi que la version de JComic que vous utilisez. Vous pouvez effacer ces informations si vous le souhaitez mais elles me sont très utiles, en particulier pour le débuggage de l\'application.
